    <exercise id="fs-id2572932" type="problem-exercises"><problem id="fs-id2572933">    <para id="import-auto-id2912658">(a) Using data from <link document="m60912" target-id="import-auto-id2866785"/>, calculate the mass converted to energy by the fission of 1.00 kg of uranium. (b) What is the ratio of mass destroyed to the original mass, <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>Δ</m:mn><m:mi fontstyle="italic">m</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">/</m:mo><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow></m:semantics></m:math>?</para></problem></exercise>
    <exercise id="fs-id1539307" type="problem-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1539308">    <para id="import-auto-id1363138">(a) Using data from <link document="m60912" target-id="import-auto-id2866785"/>, calculate the amount of mass converted to energy by the fusion of 1.00 kg of hydrogen. (b) What is the ratio of mass destroyed to the original mass, <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>Δ</m:mn><m:mi fontstyle="italic">m</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">/</m:mo><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow></m:semantics></m:math>? (c) How does this compare with <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>Δ</m:mn><m:mi fontstyle="italic">m</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">/</m:mo><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow></m:semantics></m:math> for the fission of 1.00 kg of uranium?</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-id1993570">
    <para id="import-auto-id3084938"><m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mtext>.</m:mtext>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo>
                    <m:msup>
                      <m:mtext>10</m:mtext>
                      
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo>
                            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mrow>
                      
                    </m:msup>
                  </m:mrow>
                <m:mspace width="0.25em"/>
                  <m:mtext>kg</m:mtext>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:semantics>
      </m:math> 
    </para><para id="import-auto-id2631704">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mtext>.</m:mtext>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo>
                    <m:msup>
                      <m:mtext>10</m:mtext>
                      
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo>
                            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mrow>
                      
                    </m:msup>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            
            <m:mrow/>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{7 "." 1 times "10" rSup { size 8{ - 3} } } {}</m:annotation>
        </m:semantics>
      </m:math> 
